Digital Signage
Products
Deliver Enterprise-Level Performance
We design, engineer, and install visual communication systems that solve a multitude of problems for organizations of allsizes and complexity.
Learn more






 







 
 





Hardware
RMG media players and displays offer power and performance in a cost-effective package.
learn more



 
 





Software
Make your data actionable and your content compelling with RMG digital signage software.
learn more



 
 





 
 
 
 







Hardware
RMG media players and displays offer power and performance in a cost-effective package.
learn more



 
 





Software
Make your data actionable and your content compelling with RMG digital signage software.
learn more



 
 
 
 



Benefits of Using Digital Signage Hardware and Software
Traditional signage is an outdated and ineffective means of communicating critical messages to modern audiences. RMG’s innovative software and hardware solutions offer reliability and performancein a cost-effective package.
 
 
 





Manage Internal Processes
Consolidate internal and external communications efforts, productivity reporting, and data visualization in one secure, easy-to-use contentmanagement platform.

 
 
 




Enhance Customer Experience
Guide buyers through their journey with an immersive HD or Ultra HD visual experience powered by data and analytics to influence purchasing decisions.

 
 
 




Realize ROI
Discover the ROI that our industry-leading enterprise-level visual communications solution can provide for your company, large or small.

 
 
 
 





Boost Communication Flow
Increase innovation, collaboration, and accountability with drag-and-drop messaging delivered from anywhere in the world to target audiences.

 
 
 




Inform and Entertain Viewers
Creatively display news feeds, brand messaging, video and HDTV streams, and live data all on eye-catching large displays, desktops, or mobile devices.

 
 
 




Expand Your Reach
Publish your content to a virtually endless number of endpoints around the world with our robust,scalable solution.

 
 
 
 
 



Digital Signage Systems That Work
RMG creates integrated software and hardware for managing the collection, design, scheduling, display, and delivery of critical information to a variety of visual solutions. Today, RMG customers have installed over 20,000 content management servers delivering content to over one million displays.
 
 
 
 





Our communication solutions are not stand-alone pieces of equipment, but rather complete, integrated digital signage networks. Our digital signage systems enable organizations to both manage internal processes more efficiently and also provide visitors with a comfortable, positive experience in their facilities at all times.
–


Manage Internal Processes More Efficiently







 



Components to Enhance Your Experience
 
 
 


Digital Signage Hardware

SDA media players lead the industry in reliability, performance, and security
A full range of large LCD/LED and all-in-one SmartScreen displays for the ultimate HD view
Information kiosks that put information at a guest’s fingertips
Video walls with an unsurpassed “WOW” factor
Door displays to help guests navigate to the right meeting room

 
 

Digital Signage Software

RMG Enterprise Server (RMG ES) – a sophisticated digital signage server that collects, stores, and distributes real-time information transparently
Design Studio is a web-based software suite allowing users to create and update content with ease
RMG INVIEW – a desktop and mobile application that displays centrally managed content to employee PCs and mobile devices anywhere in the world
Broadcast PC software transforms standard PCs into high functioning media player

 
 
 
 



More About Products and Solutions
 
 
 





Smart Digital Signagefor Your Business
Our digital signage networks are widely used by hospitality, financial services, higher education, healthcare, and retail organizations. With our smart digital signage, no matter your industry or market, employers can provide employees real-time visibility into the state of their operations to aid front-line decision making.

 
 
 




Solutions That IntegrateWith Your Systems
Digital signage use is gaining ground: Our digital signage wireless solutions present a clean, compelling look; our digital signage pricing produces substantial ROI; and our digital signage incorporates innovative technology enabling clients to integrate with their internal systems to produce a seamless flow of communication, whether for informing or entertaining.

 
 
 




Supported Solutionsfor Your Systems
RMG solutions are fully supported with our optional services, from the earliest design stages to ongoing systems maintenance. We have an energetic staff of highly imaginative and accomplished designers; we pull in and edit news content from thousands of local, regional, and global sources that can be fed into client facilities; we have consulting and technical teams on staff to assist in and guide the integration process with client systems; and, we can provide ongoing training and 24/7/365 technical support to help your digital signage hardware and software operate at full capacity.

 
 
 
 
 


